<div id="article">
    <h2>HTML이란 무엇인가?</h2>
    <h3><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/" target="_blank" title="html5 specification">
        Hypertext  Markup Language(HTML)</a> is the standard markup language for
        <strong>creating <u>web</u> pages and web applications.</strong>
    </h3>
    <img src="coding.jpg" width="40%">
    <p>
        <strong id="ref">1. tag</strong> : like strong, /strong covered in brackets<br>
        strong tag : to mark as bold<br>
        underline tag : to make words underlined<br>
        header tag : h1 - h6 gets smaller word size<br>
        new line tag : br tag<br>
        paragraph tag : p tag<br>
        image tag : img<br>
        list tag : li tag -> abrev of list<br>
        ul tag : <strong>parent tag of li</strong> that we must include to use li tag. = unordered list<br>
        ol tag : numbering each list. It is the parent tag of li. = ordered list<br>
        a tag : 가장 대표적인 태그. 이 태그 덕분에 웹페이지를 발견하고 최고의 검색 결과를 만들 수 있다. link(hypertext)를 위한 태그 = anchor<br>
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong id="ref">2. attribute</strong> : like src, width to give more information in tag
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong id="ref">3. structure</strong><br>
        <strong>!doctype</strong><br>
        <strong>html</strong><br>
        <strong>head tag</strong> : information about contents<br>
        title tag : search engine finds sites based on title tag, like book cover.<br>
        meta tag<br>
        <strong>/head</strong><br>
        <strong>body tag</strong> : contents<br>
        <strong>/body</strong><br>
        <strong>/html</strong><br>
    </p>
    <p>
        kakao 클론 코딩하면서 정리해두어야 할 부분 <br>
        html5의 문법 -> 화면을 구성할때 쓰이는 태그 등(header, main, nav 등)<br>
        class 명명 방식 -> BEM 및 다른 방식<br>
    </p>
</div>